{"tid":1432697,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(一帶一路) 吉爾吉斯人抗議中企污染   數十中国員工被毆","createTime":"2019-08-08T09:50:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T04:53:02.000Z","uid":184679,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"68c78617c15c22cae73168559d6553ac7fb7dfe3","tid":1432697,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:50:24.000Z","msg":"中國推動「一帶一路」戰略，引發的各種債務問題及經營衝突不斷。沿線國家吉爾吉斯的一家中資企業5日遭當地居民示威要求停工，數十名中方員工被毆打受傷，導火線據稱與環保汙染有關。<br />\n<br />\n總和自由歐洲電台（Radio Free Europe/RadioLiberty）及新華社報導，中吉礦業有限公司在吉爾吉斯經營的索爾通&mdash;薩雷（Solton-Sary）金礦，有約500名當地居民5日舉行示威集會，要求企業停工並撤離，部分集會者闖入礦區，毆打中方員工。<br />\n<br />\n衝突發生時，礦場上約有170名中國工人，其中數十人不同程度受傷。根據吉國衛生部通報，所有傷者傷勢穩定，至6日有20名中國工人住院治療，也有些當地居民受傷。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，當地居民7月份時就指責中國的礦業公司汙染當地環境，造成大批牲畜死亡。但當局檢測土壤樣品，並未發現化學物質或高劑量的輻射汙染。<br />\n<br />\n中國駐吉爾吉斯大使館6日發表聲明說，此次事件給中方人員人身和財產安全造成重大損失，已向吉方提出嚴正交涉，要求嚴懲肇事者。中方敦促吉國政府及有關部門採取切實措施，維護中國企業合法權益，確保中方人員安全，避免再次發生類似事件。<br />\n<br />\n吉爾吉斯總理阿布加濟耶夫（MukhammedkalyiAbylgaziev）已經下令針對事件調查，並警告不要將此衝突轉變為政治議題。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6809/3977783\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6809%2F3977783&d=g7cViP25SqI%2F%2FE6cIGpO722%2BFslq3%2Bj4herl9tsBg9w%3D&h=06f6f9cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6809/3977783</a>"},{"pid":"1f10636a1b5fa9424eafde190fe747e194c2d0a2","tid":1432697,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T10:01:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c24e3407e5fe4895e54c6b9f0307aa92281eef7","tid":1432697,"uid":253992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T10:01:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"481d3c93266d7a312a9572a6f946edd7c8d0b795","tid":1432697,"uid":278365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T10:02:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"670cfef5c6101bf60ae0c5e1970f527d40ab74c9","tid":1432697,"uid":228894,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T10:04:05.000Z","msg":"舔共政府都有一個共通點---背棄自己人民<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"650ad06f5d90bf7ba3e9fc0c1b016cba31767784","tid":1432697,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T15:32:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d2dc85d96f750a2348009e3ce474a4ab2b6dbc9","tid":1432697,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T04:35:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88c136a42049e10f6e6fd0cb7cc3d7b36f5281c0","tid":1432697,"uid":4964,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T04:49:19.000Z","msg":"福建人，係時候買機票出發啦"},{"pid":"376d9290e1c557e8b0c63e0f3602948dbb918e0e","tid":1432697,"uid":89869,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T04:53:02.000Z","msg":"根本有中國人嘅地方就已經係污染"}]}